#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.indices.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.indices"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:1 of
msgid "Return a tensor representing the indices of a grid."
msgstr "返回一个表示网格索引的张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:3 of
msgid ""
"Compute a tensor where the subtensors contain index values 0,1,... "
"varying only along the corresponding axis."
msgstr "计算一个张量，其子张量包含索引值 0,1,...，仅在相应轴上变化。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:6 of
msgid "The shape of the grid."
msgstr "网格的形状。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:8 of
msgid "Data type of the result."
msgstr "结果的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:10 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:13 of
msgid ""
"**grid** -- The tensor of grid indices, ``grid.shape = (len(dimensions),)"
" + tuple(dimensions)``."
msgstr ""
"**grid** -- 网格索引的张量，``grid.shape = (len(dimensions),) + tuple("
"dimensions)``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:17 of
msgid ":py:obj:`mgrid`, :py:obj:`meshgrid`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:20 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:21 of
msgid ""
"The output shape is obtained by prepending the number of dimensions in "
"front of the tuple of dimensions, i.e. if `dimensions` is a tuple ``(r0, "
"..., rN-1)`` of length ``N``, the output shape is ``(N,r0,...,rN-1)``."
msgstr ""
"输出形状是通过在维度元组前面加上维度数量得到的，即如果 `dimensions` 是"
"长度为 ``N`` 的元组 ``(r0, ..., rN-1)``，则输出形状为 ``(N,r0,...,rN-1)``"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:26 of
msgid ""
"The subtensors ``grid[k]`` contains the N-D array of indices along the "
"``k-th`` axis. Explicitly::"
msgstr "子张量 ``grid[k]`` 包含沿第 ``k`` 个轴的 N 维索引数组。显式地："

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:32 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:45 of
msgid "The indices can be used as an index into a tensor."
msgstr "这些索引可以用作张量的索引。"

#: maxframe.tensor.datasource.indices.indices:51 of
msgid ""
"Note that it would be more straightforward in the above example to "
"extract the required elements directly with ``x[:2, :3]``."
msgstr "注意，在上面的示例中，直接使用 ``x[:2, :3]`` 提取所需元素会更直接。"

